data.description: Opportunity knocks at this appealing location for work and play.  Desirable Washington Manor townhome at The Willows community offering 2 bedrooms, 1.5 baths and a total of 840 sq. ft. of comfortable living space.  Relax in the comfy yet spacious living room with beautiful vinyl plank flooring or on the nice size patio adjacent to the dining area.  Enjoy cooking in this modern updated kitchen with lots of storage space, granite counter tops, stainless steel appliances and tile flooring.  A nicely updated half bath completes this well appointed downstairs.  Upstairs you will find 2 spacious bedrooms, a full updated bath room and in-unit laundry.  Most of the interior recently painted. This home is clean, move in ready!  Lush trees line the walkways adding to the ambiance as well as a community pool, play structure, a separate laundry building and designated 2 space car lift adds to the many reasons you will want to call this home!  Certain to impress is the short distance to Greenhouse Shopping Plaza and easy access to hwy 880/238.
